1) Dial back color, border color, border width
2) Create a list of DialOrnamentShapes.
3) Add a Skin property.
4) expose properties to control the image quality.
5) Use ticks1 instead of ticks5

5) Add design time support for changing the hands, numbers and ticks.
6) Add design time support for changing the time provider.

7) The shape of the clock: Round, Square, Romb. Create a pluggable object for that.
7) Try to create a compas


tutorials:
	- Replacing the default shapes.
	- Using a custom Time Provider.


